title: Installing PCF on Azure Using Terraform
owner: Ops Manager
---


Complete the following procedures to install Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF) on Azure Using Terraform:

1. Deploy Ops Manager. See [Deploying Ops Manager on Azure Using Terraform](../om/azure/prepare-env-terraform.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director on Azure Using Terraform. See [Configuring BOSH Director on Azure Using Terraform](../om/azure/config-terraform.html).

1. (Optional) Install the IPsec add-on. See [Installing the PCF IPsec Add-On](http://docs.pivotal.io/addon-ipsec/installing.html).

1. Deploy PAS. See [Deploying PAS on Azure Using Terraform](./azure-er-config-terraform.html).